OL,3,C'Unimaginable loss': Delivery driver
OL,4,Ckilled during van theft named
OL,6,FColleagues have paid tribute to a
OL,7,F"beloved" delivery driver who was
OL,8,Fkilled while trying to stop a thief
OL,9,Fstealing his van.
OL,11,FClaudiu-Carol Kondor has been named as
OL,12,Fthe victim of the incident in Armley,
OL,13,FLeeds, on Tuesday night.
OL,15,FMr Kondor, who was in his 40s, had
OL,16,Fmade a delivery to an address in
OL,17,FAlliance Street when he returned to
OL,18,Fhis van to find a male attempting to
OL,19,Fsteal it.
