OL,3,C'Unimaginable loss': Delivery driver
OL,4,Ckilled during van theft named
OL,6,FHe was dragged along by the vehicle as
OL,7,Fhe tried to stop the vehicle being
OL,8,Ftaken. It collided with two parked
OL,9,Fcars, leaving Mr Kondor fatally
OL,10,Finjured at around 6.50pm.
OL,12,FThe van was later found abandoned
OL,13,Fabout six miles away in Highlands
OL,14,FWalk, Belle Isle.
OL,16,FAn online fundraiser has been set up
OL,17,Ffor Mr Kondor's family by Mike Neill,
OL,18,Foperations manager at SP Transport
OL,19,FGroup, where Mr Kondor worked.
