OL,3,C'Unimaginable loss': Delivery driver
OL,4,Ckilled during van theft named
OL,6,FMr Neill wrote: "It is with heavy
OL,7,Fhearts that we share the tragic news
OL,8,Fof the loss of our beloved colleague.
OL,9,FClaudiu was a dedicated and cherished
OL,10,Fmember of the SP Transport Group
OL,11,Ffamily... This unimaginable loss has
OL,12,Fleft us all devastated."
OL,14,FHe added: "Claudiu was more than just
OL,15,Fa colleague`he was a friend, a
OL,16,Fconfidant, and a valued member of our
OL,17,Fteam. His commitment to his work and
OL,18,Fthe camaraderie he brought to the
OL,19,Fworkplace will never be forgotten.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
