OL,6,F"The impact of this tragedy extends
OL,7,Ffar beyond our workplace, affecting
OL,8,Fall who had the privilege of knowing
OL,9,FClaudiu."
OL,11,FMr Kondor delivered parcels for
OL,12,Fcompanies including Amazon, who
OL,13,Fdescribed what happened as a "terrible
OL,14,Fincident".
OL,16,FMore than #3,000 has already been
OL,17,Fraised in Mr Kondor's memory. Mr Neill
OL,18,Fsaid it would be used to "alleviate
OL,19,Fsome of the financial burdens" faced
OL,20,Fby his family.
